islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[serious] <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bb/Bridge_types.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fbb%2FBridge_types.svg&h=8354d2b6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港三條都係3?<br />\n有冇2既例子</blockquote><br />\n冇, 全部都係theory/research/proposal <br />\n挪威特別有研究, 啲fjord又長又窄又深, 橋同普通隧道都難起, 佢哋重會諗起穿山隧道做運河"},{"pid":"a7506003b1429b28542656371e5341ec6553ea28","tid":380354,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"海底椰係咪係海底?"},{"pid":"af564b23b72fc8b104838a55721d398c5d521fd1","tid":380354,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔起橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人都問過呢條問題<br />\n<br />\n你要比大型船隻過黎<br />\n條橋就一定要夠高<br />\n但係海旁兩邊要預好多位去比d 車爬上去<br />\n變左景觀會有問題啦<br />\n同埋唔夠位起條咁既路"},{"pid":"f58bc364b49d11815ab28b6b14f7dc4f4537622a","tid":380354,"uid":125310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"西炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f086ca762d419dfa9f4a3e28bb1da458455906c","tid":380354,"uid":23988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"認真post 黎講<br />\n舊登有個post 講海底隧道點起<br />\n好高質"},{"pid":"3842f1085ed7070b773455e4d56e34b431044f68","tid":380354,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"呃鳩你架咋<br />\n入面冇水冇魚你都信海底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3968041ff685f53b9100a6dc731ed93f72de216","tid":380354,"uid":38651,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"細既以為海底隧道係海洋中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl